.DT
stop_teaching_skills
$MUDNAME$ Creator Help
stop_teaching_skills

.SH Name
.SP 5 5
stop_teaching_skills -  The method to call when we stop teaching skills.
.EP

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
void stop_teaching_skills(int left,
mixed bing)
.EI

.SH Parameters
.SI 5
%^BOLD%^left%^RESET%^ - the amount of time left
%^BOLD%^bing%^RESET%^ - the data associated with the command

.EI

.SH Defined in
.SI 5
/std/living/skills.c
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5

The method to call when we stop teaching skills.  THis will stop the
stuff being taught if the stop is successful, and only teach partial
amounts if we are not finished yet.
.EP

